					<a class="addthis_button_twitter"  addthis:url="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/09/inside-solid-who-will-build-the-god-platform-for-the-internet-of-things.html" addthis:title="Inside Solid: who will build the &#8220;god platform&#8221; for the Internet of Things?"></a>						

					<a class="addthis_button_google_plusone_share" addthis:url="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/09/inside-solid-who-will-build-the-god-platform-for-the-internet-of-things.html" addthis:title="Inside Solid: who will build the &#8220;god platform&#8221; for the Internet of Things?"></a>	

