        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-44284" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-44284" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>That&#8217;s my question as well; the value in something like a connected washing machine (to pick a trivial example) is overwhelmingly in its ability to wash clothes, not in its connectivity or software. The value in a smartphone is overwhelmingly in its connectivity and software.</p>
</div>
        </div>

    </li><!-- #comment-## -->
